<p>Is it just me or does anyone else get lost in the library?  Well anyway I just got mine just now and the best the best way to get this is to wait till you can handle first tier planes yard trash.  I got all my pages from PoN and PoI.  Treants seem to drop them most frequently in PoN and any of the mechs you pull to zone except the tin soldiers and the Archaics seem to drop these pages.  I will say that they seem FAR more common in PoN and I did not get a single page drop in PoD although I hear that they can.  I haven't spent much time in PoJ (I'm a cleric so I tend to like camps or at least I am used to sitting in one place) and PoJ groups that I have been in tend to move every coupla pulls.  If you can XP in PoI or PoN then these pages are going to drop anyways so yuo might as well but be warned these things will take up a slot in you inventory for a while (like over a month for me).  Remeber hat the guy that gives this quest is on the top floor.  you gotta take the elvator on the first (?) floor to get there.  Good luck all <br /></p>
